{
  "video_id": "u9hauSrihYQ",
  "title": "Why do we ask questions? Michael \"Vsauce\" Stevens at TEDxVienna",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 19626.0,
      "end_time": 25752.0,
      "text": "What is the best kind of cheese to use to catch a bear?"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 25752.0,
      "end_time": 28099.0,
      "text": "Someone knows over here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 28099.0,
      "end_time": 30894.0,
      "text": "Obviously, the answer is &quot;come here bear.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 30894.0,
      "end_time": 32052.0,
      "text": "Camembert!"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 32052.0,
      "end_time": 33167.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 33167.0,
      "end_time": 34391.0,
      "text": "Camembert!"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34391.0,
      "end_time": 37135.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 37135.0,
      "end_time": 39461.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39461.0,
      "end_time": 42834.0,
      "text": "I have a head full of cheese puns,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 42834.0,
      "end_time": 46546.0,
      "text": "but I was told I had to keep it &#39;brie&#39;-f."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46546.0,
      "end_time": 48716.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48716.0,
      "end_time": 51519.0,
      "text": "What did the piece of cheese say"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 51519.0,
      "end_time": 57417.0,
      "text": "when it looked into the mirror?"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 57417.0,
      "end_time": 60852.0,
      "text": "No. It said, &quot;Halloumi.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 60852.0,
      "end_time": 62262.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 62262.0,
      "end_time": 64382.0,
      "text": "Hello me!"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 64382.00000000001,
      "end_time": 69854.0,
      "text": "What can I say guys? I love a good pun."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 69854.0,
      "end_time": 73214.0,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 73214.0,
      "end_time": 74670.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know;"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 74670.0,
      "end_time": 78493.0,
      "text": "because puns are funny, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 78493.0,
      "end_time": 79577.0,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 79577.0,
      "end_time": 82761.0,
      "text": "Well, because there is a bit of a surprise factor."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 82761.0,
      "end_time": 87208.0,
      "text": "You feel outsmarted for a second until you get the double meaning."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 87208.0,
      "end_time": 89323.0,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 89323.0,
      "end_time": 94352.0,
      "text": "Because that&#39;s the way language works."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 94352.0,
      "end_time": 97210.0,
      "text": "OK. I get what these slides are doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 97210.0,
      "end_time": 100664.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re playing the why game"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 100664.0,
      "end_time": 103954.0,
      "text": "where you keep asking, &quot;Why, why, but why?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 103954.0,
      "end_time": 105687.0,
      "text": "after everything someone says."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 105687.0,
      "end_time": 108648.0,
      "text": "Kids do it all of the time"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 108648.0,
      "end_time": 113189.0,
      "text": "and adults should do it more often."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 113189.0,
      "end_time": 115119.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m just kidding. Don&#39;t. It&#39;s annoying."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 115119.0,
      "end_time": 118266.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 118266.0,
      "end_time": 122377.0,
      "text": "You can ask why, over, and over, and over again for ever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 122377.0,
      "end_time": 125392.0,
      "text": "even if one day, we explain"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 125392.0,
      "end_time": 127602.0,
      "text": "every physical interaction, and scientific law,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 127602.0,
      "end_time": 132681.0,
      "text": "and hope, and dream, and regret with a single elegant equation."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 132681.0,
      "end_time": 137414.0,
      "text": "You could still ask, &quot;Why? Why that equation?"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 137414.0,
      "end_time": 142059.0,
      "text": "Why doesn&#39;t the universe operate with some different equation?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 142059.0,
      "end_time": 147261.0,
      "text": "So, yes; the why game is irritating, it&#39;s annoying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 147261.0,
      "end_time": 150601.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s what I do for a living."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 150601.0,
      "end_time": 152845.0,
      "text": "Every week, for the past few years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 152845.0,
      "end_time": 157709.0,
      "text": "I have researched a big question, a funny why question."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 157709.0,
      "end_time": 160844.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve researched the science&#39;s, the mathematicsâ€™s recent theories"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 160844.0,
      "end_time": 163250.0,
      "text": "behind all kinds of things."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 163250.0,
      "end_time": 167522.0,
      "text": "I do this on my YouTube channel: Vsauce."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 167522.0,
      "end_time": 171542.0,
      "text": "So, Vsauce, in the last couple of years, has grown phenomenally."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 171542.0,
      "end_time": 173282.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s hard to believe."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 173282.0,
      "end_time": 177437.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m now doing more than 30 million views every single month,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 177437.0,
      "end_time": 179657.0,
      "text": "with five and a half subscribers"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 179657.0,
      "end_time": 184437.0,
      "text": "growing more than 10,000 new subscribers every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 184437.0,
      "end_time": 186890.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s awesome. I love it."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 186890.0,
      "end_time": 190486.0,
      "text": "I get to ask some pretty ridiculous questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 190486.0,
      "end_time": 194134.0,
      "text": "For instance, &quot;Is anything real?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 194134.0,
      "end_time": 197936.0,
      "text": "Come on! How can you possible answer that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 197936.0,
      "end_time": 199564.0,
      "text": "Well, that&#39;s not really the point."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 199564.0,
      "end_time": 202176.0,
      "text": "The point is to bring people in with a great question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 202176.0,
      "end_time": 204769.0,
      "text": "make them curious, and once they&#39;re there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 204769.0,
      "end_time": 208775.0,
      "text": "accidentally teach them a whole bunch of things about the universe."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 208775.0,
      "end_time": 210495.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 210495.0,
      "end_time": 216930.0,
      "text": "Some examples of other questions I&#39;ve asked:"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 216930.0,
      "end_time": 220150.0,
      "text": "how much does a shadow weigh?"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 220150.0,
      "end_time": 226432.0,
      "text": "What does it mean to ask a question like that, &quot;What us a shadow?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 226432.0,
      "end_time": 229252.0,
      "text": "What color is a mirror?"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 229252.0,
      "end_time": 231765.0,
      "text": "In answering this question, you could explain a lot"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 231765.0,
      "end_time": 235221.0,
      "text": "about specular reflection, the physics of light."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 235221.0,
      "end_time": 239233.0,
      "text": "This is one of my favorites, &quot;Why are things creepy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 239233.0,
      "end_time": 242259.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 242259.0,
      "end_time": 246271.0,
      "text": "I often go into psychology - that&#39;s more where my background is in -"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 246271.0,
      "end_time": 252180.0,
      "text": "but a question I have yet to answer, - hopefully, someone out there knows -"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 252180.0,
      "end_time": 255656.0,
      "text": "please tell me why is this called your &#39;bottom&#39;"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 255656.0,
      "end_time": 257976.0,
      "text": "if it&#39;s technically in the middle of your body?"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 257976.0,
      "end_time": 259173.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 259173.0,
      "end_time": 260301.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s ridiculous."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 260301.0,
      "end_time": 262021.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s a really good question."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 262021.00000000003,
      "end_time": 268085.0,
      "text": "I ask questions all of the time, but today, this is my question."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 268085.0,
      "end_time": 271102.0,
      "text": "Why do we ask questions?"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 271102.0,
      "end_time": 272901.0,
      "text": "Seriously. I mean, what&#39;s the point?"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 272901.0,
      "end_time": 276577.0,
      "text": "Who cares why things are creepy? They just are."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 276577.0,
      "end_time": 279431.0,
      "text": "Who cares why this is called my bottom?"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 279431.0,
      "end_time": 285054.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s gross, don&#39;t do that anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 285054.0,
      "end_time": 287380.0,
      "text": "Questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 287380.0,
      "end_time": 292863.0,
      "text": "How do I get people to care about these questions?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 292863.0,
      "end_time": 297022.0,
      "text": "Especially people who think that learning is boring."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 297022.0,
      "end_time": 303472.0,
      "text": "I like to believe that the limits of what you can be interested in"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 303472.0,
      "end_time": 305351.0,
      "text": "are unlimited."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 305351.0,
      "end_time": 307720.0,
      "text": "And this is my story."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 307720.0,
      "end_time": 310805.0,
      "text": "I began making YouTube videos about six years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 310805.0,
      "end_time": 314384.0,
      "text": "but only recently did I start making explanatory videos."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 314384.0,
      "end_time": 316214.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve no idea what took me so long."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 316214.0,
      "end_time": 319298.0,
      "text": "I have been explaining things my entire life."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 319298.0,
      "end_time": 324018.0,
      "text": "Except, usually, I did it alone, out loud."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 324018.0,
      "end_time": 327619.0,
      "text": "I talk to myself when I&#39;m alone; all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 327619.0,
      "end_time": 330515.0,
      "text": "If you snuck up on me when I didn&#39;t think anyone was around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 330515.0,
      "end_time": 334862.0,
      "text": "you would overhear me explaining the most mundane stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 334862.0,
      "end_time": 338822.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s kind of weird, maybe."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 338822.0,
      "end_time": 342376.0,
      "text": "OK, it&#39;s really weird, but for me, it is a great way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 342376.0,
      "end_time": 346781.0,
      "text": "for me to know that I kind of know more what I&#39;m talking about"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 346781.0,
      "end_time": 351238.0,
      "text": "if I can verbally explain it."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 351238.0,
      "end_time": 352724.0,
      "text": "As Albert Einstein said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 352724.0,
      "end_time": 357554.0,
      "text": "&quot;If you can&#39;t explain it simply, you don&#39;t understand it well enough.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 357554.0,
      "end_time": 362453.0,
      "text": "When I was a teenager, I discovered a competitive speaking program"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 362453.0,
      "end_time": 364784.0,
      "text": "and one of the events was informative speaking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 364784.0,
      "end_time": 369019.0,
      "text": "where you literally got to write a speech explaining something to judges,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 369019.0,
      "end_time": 372594.0,
      "text": "and then you were given points and medals if you were good enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 372594.0,
      "end_time": 380022.0,
      "text": "My very first informative speech ever was about ketchup:"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 380022.0,
      "end_time": 383452.0,
      "text": "the history of ketchup. the etymology of the name,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 383452.0,
      "end_time": 387334.0,
      "text": "its legal status, the physics of its viscosity, and how it flowed."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 387334.0,
      "end_time": 390601.0,
      "text": "It was super nerdy stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 390601.0,
      "end_time": 395936.0,
      "text": "But at my very, very first public speaking tournament"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 395936.0,
      "end_time": 398584.0,
      "text": "I took first place."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 398584.0,
      "end_time": 399720.0,
      "text": "Hey!"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 399720.0,
      "end_time": 401534.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 401534.0,
      "end_time": 402664.0,
      "text": "Look at that guy."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 402664.0,
      "end_time": 405844.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 405844.0,
      "end_time": 410170.0,
      "text": "Some of the hair here moved down here, but other than that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 410170.0,
      "end_time": 411849.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m the same guy."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 411849.0,
      "end_time": 416432.0,
      "text": "Seriously, I&#39;m still doing the same thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 416432.0,
      "end_time": 420749.0,
      "text": "To be at that tournament and to see the expression on someone&#39;s face"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 420749.0,
      "end_time": 426075.0,
      "text": "when they suddenly understand and are fascinated by something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 426075.0,
      "end_time": 429510.0,
      "text": "in the same way that you are"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 429510.0,
      "end_time": 430940.0,
      "text": "is a phenomenal feeling."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 430940.0,
      "end_time": 432822.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve learned two things from this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 432822.0,
      "end_time": 436091.0,
      "text": "first of all, people love a good explanation."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 436091.0,
      "end_time": 437631.0,
      "text": "They hunt them down."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 437631.0,
      "end_time": 441876.0,
      "text": "Even people who say they hate learning, and hate books, and all that stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 441876.0,
      "end_time": 444060.0,
      "text": "pff, they love explanations."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 444060.0,
      "end_time": 447905.0,
      "text": "Second of all, if you look closely enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 447905.0,
      "end_time": 449897.0,
      "text": "and you take the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 449897.0,
      "end_time": 453813.0,
      "text": "anything can be interesting to anyone"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 453813.0,
      "end_time": 458880.0,
      "text": "because everything is related in some way to something they care about."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 458880.0,
      "end_time": 460597.0,
      "text": "Richard Feynman called"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 460597.0,
      "end_time": 465983.0,
      "text": "&quot;the pleasure of finding things out&quot; a &quot;kick in the discovery.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 465983.0,
      "end_time": 469688.0,
      "text": "And I agree, but I think there might be a little bit more to that."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 469688.0,
      "end_time": 471681.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s get rid of this picture of me."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 471681.0,
      "end_time": 476495.0,
      "text": "We want to express ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 476495.0,
      "end_time": 478363.0,
      "text": "everyone wants to express themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 478363.0,
      "end_time": 481761.0,
      "text": "They do it through the music they listen to, the clothing they wear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 481761.0,
      "end_time": 486180.0,
      "text": "the way they act, but they also do it with knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 486180.0,
      "end_time": 489261.0,
      "text": "The things they know about the stuff they like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 489261.0,
      "end_time": 491928.0,
      "text": "Their interests, their hobbies."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 491928.0,
      "end_time": 494731.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve noticed that the most operative motive"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 494731.0,
      "end_time": 499979.0,
      "text": "behind someone sharing one of my videos, promoting me by word of mouth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 499979.0,
      "end_time": 504346.0,
      "text": "isn&#39;t so much about me as it is about them."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 504346.0,
      "end_time": 508642.0,
      "text": "&quot;Hey! Look what I found!&quot;, &quot;I like this.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 508642.0,
      "end_time": 513424.0,
      "text": "&quot;I am like this.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 513424.0,
      "end_time": 516900.0,
      "text": "Whenever you share a video, whenever you share anything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 516900.0,
      "end_time": 521609.0,
      "text": "a few of the attributes of that thing reflect back onto you."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 521609.00000000006,
      "end_time": 527840.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve found that one of the best ways to gain attentive listeners"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 527840.0,
      "end_time": 532524.0,
      "text": "is not to be who you think your audience wants you to be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 532524.0,
      "end_time": 536186.0,
      "text": "but instead, to say, and make, and show things"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 536186.0,
      "end_time": 545556.0,
      "text": "that allow your audience or your students to be who they want to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 545556.0,
      "end_time": 549792.0,
      "text": "I once discussed in a video,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 549792.0,
      "end_time": 554374.0,
      "text": "&quot;Why the sky is blue?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 554374.0,
      "end_time": 558755.0,
      "text": "And backstage, when I was going through what I want to to talk about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 558755.0,
      "end_time": 560144.0,
      "text": "I ran into this girl."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 560144.0,
      "end_time": 563356.0,
      "text": "This seriously actually happened backstage, go find her."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 563356.0,
      "end_time": 567161.0,
      "text": "I said, &quot;Do you know why the sky is blue?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 567161.0,
      "end_time": 571494.0,
      "text": "She said, &quot;I think I used to know, but it didn&#39;t really mattered.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 571494.0,
      "end_time": 573510.0,
      "text": "Exactly. Exactly."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 573510.0,
      "end_time": 575592.0,
      "text": "And I knew that was going to be a problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 575592.0,
      "end_time": 577233.0,
      "text": "It turns out that the sky is blue"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 577233.0,
      "end_time": 580701.0,
      "text": "because of the way light scatters in our atmosphere."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 580701.0,
      "end_time": 582626.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called Rayleigh scattering."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 582626.0,
      "end_time": 587446.0,
      "text": "A light of shorter wave lengths scatters more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 587446.0,
      "end_time": 589170.0,
      "text": "so, greens, blues, and violets."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 589170.0,
      "end_time": 591759.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why when you look at the sky away from the Sun,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 591759.0,
      "end_time": 594000.0,
      "text": "you see this beautiful sky blue;"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 594000.0,
      "end_time": 596492.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s all of those shorter wave lengths combining."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 596492.0,
      "end_time": 599819.0,
      "text": "When you look directly at the Sun - which you shouldn&#39;t do very often;"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 599819.0,
      "end_time": 601209.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t do it ever -"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 601209.0,
      "end_time": 605460.0,
      "text": "you see the longer wave lengths which are surviving that scattering."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 605460.0,
      "end_time": 608928.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why the Sun looks yellow during the day."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 608928.0,
      "end_time": 612541.0,
      "text": "Of course, when the Sun&#39;s light needs to travel through a whole lot of air"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 612541.0,
      "end_time": 613767.0,
      "text": "to get into your eyeball,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 613767.0,
      "end_time": 615834.0,
      "text": "a lot of scattering occurs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 615834.0,
      "end_time": 619280.0,
      "text": "and only really, really long wave lengths make it all the way there"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 619280.0,
      "end_time": 620490.0,
      "text": "directly from the Sun,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 620490.0,
      "end_time": 625561.0,
      "text": "which is why it looks orange, or sometimes red at sunrise or sunset."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 625561.0,
      "end_time": 629375.0,
      "text": "I think that&#39;s really cool, but obviously, some people"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 629375.0,
      "end_time": 632338.0,
      "text": "- including someone backstage right now -, don&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 632338.0,
      "end_time": 635809.0,
      "text": "Or maybe they already know it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 635809.0,
      "end_time": 639260.0,
      "text": "or could probably figure out if they thought about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 639260.0,
      "end_time": 640578.0,
      "text": "So what do you do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 640578.0,
      "end_time": 643601.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m trying to collect the largest audience possible that I can,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 643601.0,
      "end_time": 648385.0,
      "text": "I want to appeal to and attract as many people as possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 648385.0,
      "end_time": 652218.0,
      "text": "So what I do is I camp out with the subject."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 652218.0,
      "end_time": 654470.0,
      "text": "In this case, Rayleigh scattering."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 654470.0,
      "end_time": 657419.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve learned as much about it as I can."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 657419.0,
      "end_time": 659696.0,
      "text": "What else is it responsible for?"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 659696.0,
      "end_time": 664498.0,
      "text": "Who is it named after? Who did he love?"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 664498.0,
      "end_time": 667413.0,
      "text": "Whatever I can find that could become a great hook"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 667413.0,
      "end_time": 670567.0,
      "text": "to bring in just the right person."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 670567.0,
      "end_time": 673583.0,
      "text": "So, in this case, I&#39;ve read about Rayleigh scattering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 673583.0,
      "end_time": 678272.0,
      "text": "and I realized-- I didn&#39;t realize, I learned,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 678272.0,
      "end_time": 684702.0,
      "text": "that blue eyes are blue for the exact same reason."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 684702.0,
      "end_time": 687857.0,
      "text": "Blue eyes do not have blue pigment in them."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 687857.0,
      "end_time": 691482.0,
      "text": "Ouch! That would hurt if that was real."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 691482.0,
      "end_time": 693536.0,
      "text": "Blue eyes don&#39;t have blue pigment in them"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 693536.0,
      "end_time": 697256.0,
      "text": "any more than the air has blue pigment in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 697256.0,
      "end_time": 702155.0,
      "text": "If you were to rip out my iris, I would be like, &quot;Ouch!&quot; but then"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 702155.0,
      "end_time": 703465.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 703465.0,
      "end_time": 707300.0,
      "text": "if you grounded it up into a fine powder, it wouldn&#39;t be blue anymore"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 707300.0,
      "end_time": 711095.0,
      "text": "it would be a dull brownish-blackish color."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 711095.0,
      "end_time": 714078.0,
      "text": "Instead, blue eyes are blue because at a microscopic level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 714078.0,
      "end_time": 716364.0,
      "text": "their texture scatters light"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 716364.0,
      "end_time": 720594.0,
      "text": "just like the air in our atmosphere scatters the Sun&#39;s light"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 720594.0,
      "end_time": 723024.0,
      "text": "to make the sky blue."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 723024.0,
      "end_time": 725806.0,
      "text": "Maybe you already know why the sky is blue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 725806.0,
      "end_time": 727303.0,
      "text": "maybe you don&#39;t care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 727303.0,
      "end_time": 729973.0,
      "text": "but maybe you will be fascinated by something like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 729973.0,
      "end_time": 732814.0,
      "text": "This is why my episodes often seem to go all over the place."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 732814.0,
      "end_time": 736156.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not just because I&#39;m crazy it&#39;s also because I want to have"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 736156.0,
      "end_time": 738012.0,
      "text": "as many hooks out as possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 738012.0,
      "end_time": 741309.0,
      "text": "to catch as many people and to make them interested."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 741309.0,
      "end_time": 744340.0,
      "text": "I once did a video about rainbows."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 744340.0,
      "end_time": 747122.0,
      "text": "I thought, &quot;Some people might think rainbows are lame.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 747122.0,
      "end_time": 750488.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll teach about rainbows."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 750488.0,
      "end_time": 754292.0,
      "text": "What other types of bows are there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 754292.0,
      "end_time": 757971.0,
      "text": "Well, like when a string, like a knot..."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 757971.0,
      "end_time": 760501.0,
      "text": "Is a bow a knot?"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 760501.0,
      "end_time": 765186.0,
      "text": "Why do headphones always get tied up into knots?"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 765186.0,
      "end_time": 768344.0,
      "text": "I researched the mathematics behind this; it&#39;s fascinating."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 768344.0,
      "end_time": 771396.0,
      "text": "([Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 771396.0,
      "end_time": 773206.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll spare you all of the details;"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 773206.0,
      "end_time": 775690.0,
      "text": "also, this will allow you to go check out my videos"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 775690.0,
      "end_time": 779292.0,
      "text": "and give me many, many views rather than just one."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 779292.0,
      "end_time": 785249.0,
      "text": "In the 1950s, Harold Edgerton took a series of amazing pictures"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 785249.0,
      "end_time": 787024.0,
      "text": "of nuclear explosions."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 787024.0,
      "end_time": 788874.0,
      "text": "This is a detonation"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 788874.0,
      "end_time": 790803.0,
      "text": "just milliseconds after happening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 790803.0,
      "end_time": 795293.0,
      "text": "with an exposure time of one billionth of a second."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 795293.0,
      "end_time": 798775.0,
      "text": "You can see the energy of this plasma ball,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 798775.0,
      "end_time": 802605.0,
      "text": "the energy of the explosion is vaporizing the metal wires holding up the tower."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 802605.0,
      "end_time": 806225.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s where these glowing, spindly legs come form."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 806225.0,
      "end_time": 811965.0,
      "text": "His work attracted wider and new interest to physical phenomenon"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 811965.0,
      "end_time": 813815.0,
      "text": "simply because he featured something"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 813815.0,
      "end_time": 817515.0,
      "text": "that people couldn&#39;t help but want to look at."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 817515.0,
      "end_time": 820363.0,
      "text": "A moment you couldn&#39;t witness alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 820363.0,
      "end_time": 825130.0,
      "text": "He famously said, &quot;The trick to education"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 825130.0,
      "end_time": 827554.0,
      "text": "is to teach in such a way"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 827554.0,
      "end_time": 831250.0,
      "text": "that people only find out they&#39;re learning when it&#39;s too late.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 831250.0,
      "end_time": 832724.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 832724.0,
      "end_time": 834045.0,
      "text": "It works for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 834045.0,
      "end_time": 836779.0,
      "text": "So recently, I took on the most difficult question ever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 836779.0,
      "end_time": 838797.0,
      "text": "but also the most requested,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 838797.0,
      "end_time": 846049.0,
      "text": "&quot;How do I know that the colors I see are the same to you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 846049.0,
      "end_time": 849142.0,
      "text": "How do I know that when I look at something red,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 849142.0,
      "end_time": 852235.0,
      "text": "you don&#39;t look at the same thing and see what I would call green,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 852235.0,
      "end_time": 855115.0,
      "text": "but you call it red because that&#39;s what you&#39;ve always heard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 855115.0,
      "end_time": 857375.0,
      "text": "and we both agree, and go on our separate lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 857375.0,
      "end_time": 862315.0,
      "text": "never knowing just how different our perceptions were."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 862315.0,
      "end_time": 865555.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no such thing as a stupid question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 865555.0,
      "end_time": 868058.0,
      "text": "but there are questions that makes us feel stupid."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 868058.0,
      "end_time": 869550.0,
      "text": "This is one of them"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 869550.0,
      "end_time": 873900.0,
      "text": "because there is no way for me to crawl inside someone else&#39;s mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 873900.0,
      "end_time": 876760.0,
      "text": "to see the world as they see it."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 876760.0,
      "end_time": 879230.0,
      "text": "I thought that might be frustrating to my viewers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 879230.0,
      "end_time": 881126.0,
      "text": "that there really wasn&#39;t a good answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 881126.0,
      "end_time": 883047.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t finish this once and for all."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 883047.0,
      "end_time": 887217.0,
      "text": "So I started looking more generally into questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 887217.0,
      "end_time": 889929.0,
      "text": "And the more I read about them, and their history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 889929.0,
      "end_time": 897292.0,
      "text": "the more I realized that questions might be quite unique to humans."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 897292.0,
      "end_time": 903492.0,
      "text": "Apes that have been taught to use sign language can communicate with us."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 903492.0,
      "end_time": 907174.0,
      "text": "They can answer complex questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 907174.0,
      "end_time": 910714.0,
      "text": "they can convey novel thoughts, and they can express their emotions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 910714.0,
      "end_time": 913759.0,
      "text": "but an ape who knows sign language"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 913759.0,
      "end_time": 921979.0,
      "text": "has never been observed to ask a question."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 921979.0,
      "end_time": 926378.0,
      "text": "Soliciting information from an organism belies this assumption"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 926378.0,
      "end_time": 930623.0,
      "text": "that other organisms, in some way, have access to information that you don&#39;t;"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 930623.0,
      "end_time": 933896.0,
      "text": "that they have different, unique intentions or desires."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 933896.0,
      "end_time": 935696.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s often called the Theory of Mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 935696.0,
      "end_time": 940922.0,
      "text": "and it is incredibly difficult to show that animals have such a thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 940922.0,
      "end_time": 943609.0,
      "text": "But of course, we intuitively feel that we do."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 943609.0,
      "end_time": 945656.0,
      "text": "Chimpanzees are clever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 945656.0,
      "end_time": 950876.0,
      "text": "but they fail a pretty simple, seeming test - deciding who to go to"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 950876.0,
      "end_time": 954122.0,
      "text": "to get food that&#39;s been hiding in a room:"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 954122.0,
      "end_time": 958733.0,
      "text": "a person who was literally in the room and saw where the food was hidden,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 958733.0,
      "end_time": 961233.0,
      "text": "or a person who was also in the room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 961233.0,
      "end_time": 966043.0,
      "text": "but has had a bucket on their head all day."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 966043.0,
      "end_time": 973432.0,
      "text": "Whether or not animals have the capacity to ask questions is still being debated."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 973432.0,
      "end_time": 980590.0,
      "text": "But after reading all of this, I realized that questions are very special."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 980590.0,
      "end_time": 984079.0,
      "text": "We ask them because it&#39;s fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 984079.0,
      "end_time": 987156.0,
      "text": "Learning things is a fun experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 987156.0,
      "end_time": 990176.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s what Feynman called, &quot;a kick in the discovery.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 990176.0,
      "end_time": 991451.0,
      "text": "We also ask questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 991451.0,
      "end_time": 995731.0,
      "text": "because learning things allows us to explore what we like"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 995731.0,
      "end_time": 999107.0,
      "text": "and to show off what we know about it, to show what we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 999107.0,
      "end_time": 1003971.0,
      "text": "But we also ask questions because we can;"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 1003970.0,
      "end_time": 1010104.0,
      "text": "because perhaps uniquely here on Earth, we know that other people can help."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 1010100.0,
      "end_time": 1013818.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s a great reason to ask more and more questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 1013820.0,
      "end_time": 1018424.0,
      "text": "to celebrate more and more whys."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 1018430.0,
      "end_time": 1020590.0,
      "text": "We all want to be &quot;kicked in the discovery,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 1020590.0,
      "end_time": 1024336.0,
      "text": "it feels great, but we don&#39;t all have a discovery in the same place."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 1024329.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1027502.9999999999,
      "text": "Taking the time to find where someone&#39;s discovery is"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 1027510.0,
      "end_time": 1029459.0,
      "text": "so you can give them a kick there"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 1029450.0,
      "end_time": 1036377.0,
      "text": "isn&#39;t just about whys, it&#39;s also a very wise thing to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 1036380.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1038057.0000000001,
      "text": "And as always, thanks for watching."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 1038060.0,
      "end_time": 1048060.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}